data.description: Nestled on a coveted corner lot! This charming 3-bedroom property next to a greenbelt is waiting for you in the lovely neighborhood of Tartesso! The open-concept layout is designed for seamless & easy access to everyday living. Offering an inviting living room, soothing palette, tile flooring, & recessed lighting. Cooking is a delight in this impeccable kitchen showcasing dark wood cabinets, stainless steel appliances, granite counters, and an island w/a breakfast bar. The carpeted main suite is a perfect retreat, boasting an ensuite w/dual sinks & a walk-in closet. Imagine wonderful mornings in the serene backyard, providing a relaxing covered patio w/extended pavers & artificial turf. Hurry, before it's gone from the market!
